WEBVTT

00:00.873 --> 00:02.873
Previously on Greenleaf.

00:04.607 --> 00:06.607
Grace, what happened?

00:07.475 --> 00:08.747
Dady shoot Mac.

00:08.781 --> 00:10.781
This is Sophia's father, Ray.

00:10.793 --> 00:13.028
Our custody agreement
says I am to be consulted

00:13.062 --> 00:14.730
<i>if you take her across the state line.</i>

00:14.764 --> 00:16.431
<i>I'm taking her back to Phoenix.</i>

00:16.466 --> 00:18.166
Tell me what is going on.

00:18.201 --> 00:20.102
I'm sorry, Mae. I can't.

00:20.136 --> 00:22.337
Lady Mae's annual luncheon
is coming up in a few weeks.

00:22.372 --> 00:24.039
I can't wait.

00:24.073 --> 00:25.607
Kevin: <i>I just want to make people feel</i>

00:25.641 --> 00:27.008
like I always wanted to feel...

00:27.043 --> 00:28.276
cared for.

00:28.311 --> 00:29.745
It's working.

00:29.779 --> 00:31.127
Until you come clean with me

00:31.162 --> 00:33.215
about whatever's been going on with you,

00:33.249 --> 00:34.282
I want you out of our bed.

00:34.317 --> 00:36.451
<i>If you don't do it soon,</i>

00:36.486 --> 00:38.019
<i>I want you out of the house.</i>

